{"tid":1883994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局 ： 職員同確診者開會時有戴口罩 所以無需要隔離","createTime":"2020-02-17T10:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T03:17:17.000Z","uid":22556,"like":37,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"de2fc71f7eb0587fe480bc44b76f2653b0745a70","tid":1883994,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，衛生署今日宣佈再多一宗確診及兩宗初步確診。衞生署及醫管局今日證實，昨日確診的 54 歲太古城工程師，及其今日初步確診的 45 歲男同事，二人曾到醫管局大樓開會，共有 5 名醫管局人員出席會議。被追問與會人士身份，是否涉及醫管局高層等，當局無正面回應，但強調會議上各人有戴口罩 ，目前沒有員工需要隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/5-%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%84%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4-%E6%9C%89%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F5-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=dcd8e2b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F5-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%25AF